OL,3,CSee how you compare as women paid less
OL,4,Cthan men in key sectors
OL,6,FIn most sectors across Jersey, women
OL,7,Freceive a lower salary than men on
OL,8,Faverage.
OL,10,FThe overall gender pay gap is getting
OL,11,Fsmaller, but still stands at 5.4%.
OL,13,FIt also varies wildly between
OL,14,Fdifferent jobs and ages, according to
OL,15,Fthe report from Statistics Jersey,
OL,16,Fwhich covers the 12 months up to June
OL,17,F2025.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
