OL,3,CSee how you compare as women paid less
OL,4,Cthan men in key sectors
OL,6,FThis is a graphic on Jersey's gender
OL,7,Fpay gap by sector. If it does not
OL,8,Fdisplay correctly on your device,
OL,9,Fplease click here to view.
OL,11,FAverage hourly salary in Jersey:
OL,13,FThe general trend is that the older a
OL,14,Fwoman gets, the worse off she is
OL,15,Fcompared to a man.
OL,17,FThere is no gender pay gap for 16 to
OL,18,F19-year-olds, but by the time they
OL,19,Freach the 45 to 49 age bracket, it
OL,20,Fpeaks at 13.7%.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
