PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1773411078
OL,3,CSee how you compare as women paid less
OL,4,Cthan men in key sectors
OL,6,FHowever, there is one outlier as women
OL,7,Faged 25 to 29 earn 2.2% more than
OL,8,Ftheir male counterparts.
OL,10,FThis is a graphic on Jersey's gender
OL,11,Fpay gap by age. If it does not display
OL,12,Fcorrectly on your device, please click
OL,13,Fhere to view.
OL,15,FStatistics Jersey says: "Overall, the
OL,16,Fpattern suggests that while young men
OL,17,Fand women start on relatively equal
OL,18,Fpay, long-term career and life factors
OL,19,Flead to a growing gender pay disparity
OL,20,Fover time."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
