OL,3,CSee how you compare as women paid less
OL,4,Cthan men in key sectors
OL,6,FFor example, in the finance and legal
OL,7,Factivities sector, women start off
OL,8,Fearning more on average, but by the
OL,9,Ftime they reach the age bracket of 55
OL,10,Fto 59, men make almost two-thirds more
OL,11,Fthan their female colleagues.
OL,13,FThe full report can be viewed here.
